TITLE: Programmatically Triggering Copy and Cut Operations in Handsontable
DESCRIPTION: This example shows how to programmatically trigger copy and cut operations in Handsontable. It sets up a grid, selects a cell, and provides buttons to execute copy and cut commands.
SOURCE: https://github.com/handsontable/handsontable/blob/develop/docs/content/guides/cell-features/clipboard/clipboard.md#2025-04-10_snippet_1

LANGUAGE: html
CODE:
